OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA wet and
OL,6,Fwindy evening as rain spreads
OL,7,Fsouthwards. The rain heavy at times
OL,8,Fbut generally clearing by dawn. Gales
OL,9,Fpossible around the coasts and over
OL,10,Fthe hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright and breezy day.
OL,13,FGenerally dry, with sunny spells but
OL,14,Fthe odd light shower may drift in on
OL,15,Fthe fresh northwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
