OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFine on
OL,6,FFriday, with pleasant spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Cloudier on Saturday, with
OL,8,Fperhaps some light rain over the hills
OL,9,Fat times. Warmer and brighter again on
OL,10,FSunday.
